{"tid":412073,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"也許我不會活多一歲 Dear Jane","createTime":"2017-09-24T10:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T10:56:34.000Z","uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b50ff05264e8f13de5a8411d259b083708f0282f","tid":412073,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:48:26.000Z","msg":"也許我不會活多一歲<br />\n<br />\n作詞：林寶    作曲：Howie@Dear Jane<br />\n編：Dear Jane<br />\n監：Howie@Dear Jane / 關禮琛 / Tim@Dear Jane<br />\n<br />\n也許我 不會活多一歲 這脆弱的身軀 不足遠征攀山涉水<br />\n也許我 不會活出金句 會白流著血淚 再被時代降罪<br />\n每夜沈淀畏懼 百萬串的思緒 所有抉擇 難做對 得決定 無默許<br />\n<br />\n不會 我不會空等 做個蠢人 也沒不忿<br />\n每道裂痕 裂入我心懲罰 都想不枉此生<br />\n我只有堅持 這畢生缺陷 就算哭也是奢侈的放任<br />\n痛苦烙印 有幾個知音在共振<br />\n<br />\n也許我 不算活得乾脆 每夜徒力抗睡 拒絕承認已累<br />\n會為成就顧慮 建自騙的堡壘 這個世上 無絕對 得性命 無或許<br />\n<br />\n不會 我不會空等 做個蠢人 也沒不忿<br />\n每道裂痕 裂入我心懲罰 都想不枉此生<br />\n我只有堅持 這畢生缺陷 就算哭也是 奢侈的放任<br />\n痛苦烙印 有幾個知音在共振<br />\n<br />\n不行 誰有路不行 話意義失真 哪一個狠心 哪一次消沈<br />\n哪一句傷人 哪一個蠢得信任信心 誰負責任 誰一生<br />\n<br />\n給我 最短瞬一生 做個蠢人 也沒不忿<br />\n錯夢裡尋 我沒有的成份 都可睇清我根<br />\n我只有堅持 這畢生缺陷 就算不濟事 不屈得過分<br />\n我可面對 我的每一刻沒萬歲<br />\n<br />\n我可面對 我今生沒下歲<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/song/etxvr00w8CYQ2VjtuVjtu0X4-index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kkbox.com%2Fhk%2Ftc%2Fsong%2Fetxvr00w8CYQ2VjtuVjtu0X4-index.html&d=SmmKGvdAKZkurWpwob5GV7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=a75b06d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/song/etxvr00w8CYQ2VjtuVjtu0X4-index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n試聽 :  Spotify  / KKBOX<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n終於唔係情歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b8418b4b0855964c4f8871e2d4ceb6ecbca0cc","tid":412073,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:48:48.000Z","msg":"打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b7ea6d7691af07cebddd23e8f9b9e698cb37fe","tid":412073,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDear jane使撚打手<br />\n唔出名嘅嘢先要打手"},{"pid":"c27e241881e861c5a6f3ad58d8d2c74173ec3518","tid":412073,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:53:26.000Z","msg":"難得唔係情歌, 但啲詞好普通 , 扮係高深但其實有啲亂嚟 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8001ac0b2a6b9247749e194b2d95fa447b7c746f","tid":412073,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:53:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bf1b90f72e6b763e3fd5db4a2f0160fb593a935","tid":412073,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:53:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDear jane使撚打手<br />\n唔出名嘅嘢先要打手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪撚理條 on 9 仔啦,   block 鳩左佢好耐"},{"pid":"fbea54d85a362ab3232f956b19a76a463d13c56b","tid":412073,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:55:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger <br />\n<br />\n難得唔係情歌 <br />\n難得個曲多過少少鼓聲<br />\n交份咁既詞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c155d7647022d433e04fba3c2986bb67800b0286","tid":412073,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:56:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}